Template.Name: ATSDR_RRR
Template.Description: ATSDR Rapid Response Registry Survey Form

View.Name: ATSDR_RRR
View.CheckCode:
/* >>>Notice About Imported Check Code<<< This Check Code was imported from an Epi Info 3.x project. Review and validate the new Check Code for proper Epi Info 7.x syntax. Some commands and features are not yet available in this Epi Info 7 release.
Click 'Validate Check Code' at the top to identify and correct any errors. If you experience errors or need assistance, contact the Epi Info Help Desk at EpiInfo@cdc.gov. */
Field Q2DataSrc After IF Q2DataSrc="Registrant" THEN GOTO Q3FstName END
IF Q2DataSrc="Proxy" THEN GOTO Q3FstName END
IF Q2DataSrc="Medical/Medical Examiner's/Other Record" THEN GOTO Q3FstName END
IF Q2DataSrc="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q3FstName END
IF Q2DataSrc="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q3FstName END End-After End-Field
Field Q1English After IF Q1English="Yes" THEN GOTO Q2DataSrc END End-After End-Field
Field Q11Employment After IF Q11Employment="Not employed" THEN GOTO Q12Person1 END
IF Q11Employment="Self employed" THEN GOTO Q12Person1 END End-After End-Field
Field Q10Email After IF Q10Email="No" THEN GOTO Q11Employment END
IF Q10Email="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q11Employment END
IF Q10Email="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q11Employment END End-After End-Field
Field Q12Person1 After IF Q12Person1="No" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q12Person1="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q12Person1="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END End-After End-Field
Field Q17Person2 After IF Q17Person2="No" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q17Person2="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q17Person2="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END End-After End-Field
Field Q21P2Email After IF Q21P2Email="No" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q21P2Email="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END
IF Q21P2Email="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q22Resident END End-After End-Field
Field Q29Injured After IF Q29Injured="No" THEN GOTO Q30ChronicIll END
IF Q29Injured="Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q30ChronicIll END
IF Q29Injured="Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q30ChronicIll END End-After End-Field
Field Q30None After IF Q30None=(+) THEN GOTO Q32Pregnant END End-After End-Field
Field Q30DontKnow After IF Q30DontKnow=(+) THEN GOTO Q32Pregnant END End-After End-Field
Field Q30RefusetoAnswer After IF Q30RefusetoAnswer=(+) THEN GOTO Q32Pregnant END End-After End-Field
Field Q34Insurance1 After IF Q34Insurance1= "None" THEN GOTO Q36EvntSpec11 END
IF Q34Insurance1= "Don't Know" THEN GOTO Q36EvntSpec11 END
IF Q34Insurance1= "Refuse to Answer" THEN GOTO Q36EvntSpec11 END End-After End-Field

Field.Name: ATSDRRAPIDRESPONSEREGISTRYSURVEY

Field.Name: Q1PrefLang
Field.PromptText: If No: What language do you prefer?

Field.Name: Q8BResidents
Field.PromptText: B. How many people live at this address?

Field.Name: Q10Email
Field.PromptText: 10. (Do you/does registrant) have and email address?

Field.Name: Q12Person1
Field.PromptText: 12. Is there someone who does not live with (you/registrant) who can always reach (you/registrant)?

Field.Name: Q18P2FullName
Field.PromptText: 18. What is that person's full name?

Field.Name: Q16P1Email
Field.PromptText: 16. (Do you/does he/she) have an email address?

Field.Name: Q17Person2

Field.Name: Q22ExpStat
Field.PromptText: 22. (Were you/was registrant) exposed to this event as (CHECK ALL THAT APPLY):

Field.PromptText: 23. (Were you/was registrant) at the event site when the event started?

Field.PromptText: 25. What was the name of nearest building to (you/registrant)?

Field.PromptText: Inside a car or other vehicle

Field.PromptText: 29. As a result of the event, did (you/registrant) get injured or ill?

Field.Name: Q33Needs
Field.PromptText: 33. As a result of this event, (are you/is registrant) personally in need of any of the following?

Field.Name: Q35InsCo1

Field.PromptText: 38. INDICATE THE SEVERITY OF THE EFFECT ON REGISTRANT
